channel.title: Mtp webclient (noobfriendly) (html code)
channel.description:
PS: Here is link to mtp server http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,457959.0.html Note : THIS IS JUST TO HELP OUT PEOPLE THAT WANT A WEBCLIENT FOR MTP SERVER. I DO NOT DESERVE NOR WANT ANY CREDITS. CALL ME A DAMN LEECHER.. I DONT CARE.
Hello so i got MTP Webclient and I posted it in the download section because the MTP server is in there too.
This code was made by vince but his website that makes PI Webclient went down so I wanted to release the webclient.
So first of all, here is the html code for it:
[code]<center><applet name=client width=765 height=503 archive="http://armyscape.ucoz.com/loader.zip" code="client.class">
<PARAM name='java_arguments' value='-Xmx700m'> <PARAM name='server_name' value='Armyscape PVP'> <PARAM name='detail' value='low'> <PARAM name='ip' value='Server Ip'> <PARAM name='port' value='43594'> <PARAM name='background_image' value='http://i31.tinypic.com/k17tpx.png'> <PARAM name='headicons' value='prayer'></applet></center>[/code]
The client files, sprites and cachedownloader has been uploaded to my website but if you want to host it,
you can download the files at : http://uppit.com/p8liv2u34xce/loader.zip
What did I do? -Host the main files -Rehost the cache -Supply html code
Credits:
0.5% to me for leaching it and uploading it :P
Well.. i gues Vince im not sure lol... Added Picture: [img]http://img151.imageshack.us/img151/4153/piwebclient.png[/img]

UHmmm it isnt working im getting error to connecting server retrying in 5 4 3 whatever
but i just copied the Html and set ip as 127.0.0.1 and ntohing happend please help :D[/quote]

Your IP is not 127.0.0.1 That is a system default for programs installed on your computer to communicate with each other rather than having to send data to the internet, and then back to the computer. Goto http://www.whatsmyip.org/ The IP of your computer that you’re using shows up at the top of the screen there. Take that and put it where your 127.0.0.1 is in your code.
